Description: SONiC to D-Bus inventory bridge for ASPEED BMC
 Bridges SONiC data sources (Redis, platform.json, FRU EEPROMs)
 to OpenBMC-compatible D-Bus interfaces, enabling bmcweb to
 serve Redfish endpoints without modification.
 .
 This daemon is specifically designed for ASPEED ARM64 BMC
 platforms running SONiC with limited database/service availability.

